data.description: Location, location, location! Your private oasis features an open floorplan, vauted ceiling in the Great Room & lots of natural lighting. The Primary Bedroom on the main features a tray ceiling & luxury bath with a whirlpool tub & cathedral ceiling. There is also 1 other bedroom on the main with it's own full bath.The gourmet kitchen includes a brand new gas range & center island with granite counters. There are 2 gas fireplaces to keep you cozy; 1 in the Great Room & in the keeping Room. Upstairs boasts 2 additional Bedrooms, 1 full baths & a Bonus Room. There's lots of storage with 2 pull-down attics & a walk-in attic. You'll love relaxing in your private fenced backyard with a fire pit & beautiful stone cooking area with a built-in mini fridge & room for a ceramic cooker! Garage entheusiasts  will love the built in workbench, cabinets & generator electrical hook-up outlet & more storage racks in the ceiling of garage. New Roof in 2020; fence in 2023; Hot water heater new in 2023.
